  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will explore and document alternative livelihoods options (composting, refusing and recycling) and agricutlural methods that can contribute to better use of natural resources. The project will design and pilot a model for how to increased community understanding of and capacities to address climate change related disaster risks and its gendered dimentions, at local level in Anuradhapura</narrative>
  </description>
